| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7410 — Recovery Inhibition (kairos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 28d826a8-5ded-519f-b106-5cdfbf9f4469"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
